_sText:
now THIS is shitposting!

idk what this even is, but Metro sent me a weird vmf while I was at Insomnia in 2016 that morphed into some weird escape map over the course of the weekend.

It has driveable bendy buses, helicopters, rocket launchers, fighter jets, and some sort of passenger jet.

As a map it does work, it picks a rooftop for the team to get to, and then you can play around until time up.
